    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 02 \u2014 CONTEXT & ROUTING\n\nLoads the Supabase knowledge base, builds the final prompt and routes the request:\n\n- Technical \u2192 APIs, Supabase, debugging, security\n- Strategy \u2192 pricing, proposals, ROI, clients\n- General \u2192 workflow design and automation guidance",
